            <div class="title">
              <h1>
                Madrasah<span>Mahabbah</span>
                <span class="sub">Learn. <span>Love.</span> Live.</span>
              </h1>
            </div>

            <div class="welcome">
              <div class="alpha">
                <p>
                  <strong class="mm">Madrasah<span>Mahabbah</span></strong> is many things. But it is nothing if it is not a <em>family</em>. Because the smallest and biggest part of our ummah is <em>family</em>. It is when we are a <em>family</em> that we truly <em>learn,</em> <em>love</em> and <em>live.</em>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

      </section>

      <!-- SECTION: PILLARS -->
